    <item>
      <title>瑞士冷冻俄罗斯资产塔利跃升至84亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/swiss-froze-28-more-russian-assets-in-past-year-following-eu</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士当局冻结的俄罗斯资产价值跃升至74亿瑞士法郎（84亿美元），因为该国对数百名被视为接近克里姆林宫的俄罗斯个人和公司采取了进一步的欧洲联盟的制裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/swiss-froze-28-more-russian-assets-in-past-year-following-eu</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 07:41:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟对特朗普全球关税罢工的“强大计划”的重视</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/eu-readies-strong-plan-against-trump-s-global-tariff-strike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟表示，如果唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）遵循他的威胁，将利用广泛的选择来对美国进行报复，并在本周本周在集团上征收所谓的互惠关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/eu-readies-strong-plan-against-trump-s-global-tariff-strike</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 07:39:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
